<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About page</title>
    <style>
      .navbar {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 16px 32px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffe0ec 0%, #f4f4f4 100%);
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e0b7c6;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(255, 192, 203, 0.08);
      }
      .navbar .user-info {
        font-size: 17px;
        color: #b03a5b;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .navbar a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #b03a5b;
        margin-left: 18px;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }
      .navbar a:hover {
        color: #e75480;
      }

      body {
        background: #fff0f6;
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      body p {
        border-radius: 24px;
        margin: 32px auto;
        max-width: 600px;
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffe0ec 0%, #ffd6e0 100%);
        padding: 28px 24px;
        color: #5a2a41;
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(255, 192, 203, 0.12);
      }
      body h1 {
        text-align: center;
        color: #b03a5b;
        margin-top: 40px;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .navbar {
          padding: 12px 10px;
        }
        body h1 {
          margin-top: 18px;
          font-size: 1.7rem;
        }
        body p {
          margin: 18px 8px;
          padding: 18px 8px;
          font-size: 1rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <%- include("header.ejs") %>
  <body>
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>
      Welcome to <strong>GlowMe Beauty Parlour</strong>!<br />
      We are dedicated to providing the best beauty and<br />
      grooming services to our clients. Our team of professionals is
      passionate<br />
      about helping you look and feel your best. <br />At our salon, we offer a
      wide range of services, including haircuts,<br />
      styling, coloring, manicures, pedicures, and more. We use high-quality<br />
      products to ensure the best results for our clients. <br /><strong
        >Thank you for choosing us. We look forward to serving you!</strong
      >
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
